---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Docs" description="Reference docs for my setup, workflow, and career context.">
  <section class="hero-surface hero-grid-lines reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <p class="eyebrow">Documentation</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Docs</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-zinc-300">
      These are the pages I keep reopening during real work: setup notes, workflow context, and career background behind the posts.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 reveal reveal-delay-2">
    <a class="interactive-card card-link-block p-6" href="/docs/setup">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-signal">/docs/setup</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">Setup</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">What I run, how it is wired, and what changed most recently.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-muted">Open setup reference</p>
    </a>

    <a class="interactive-card card-link-block p-6" href="/docs/career">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-signal">/docs/career</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100">Career</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">How I got from PowerShell scripts to platform and agent workflow engineering.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-muted">Open career context</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
